{"id": 411, "date": "1987-01-09T11:00:49", "date_gmt": "1987-01-09T19:00:49", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=411"}, "modified": "2026-06-03T17:07:16", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-04T00:07:16", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-gaslight-anthem-and-bruce-springsteen-the-59-sound", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/01/09/meeting-across-the-river-gaslight-anthem-and-bruce-springsteen-the-59-sound/", "title": {"rendered": "The &#8217;59 Sound"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>It&#8217;s hard to find a more perfectly suited pairing for Bruce than the very-Springsteen-influenced Gaslight Anthem. It&#8217;s hard to tell who&#8217;s having more fun in this 2009 HD clip&#8211;Brian and Bruce are clearly both having a ball.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/djdRSffcI9E?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>&#8220;The &#8217;59 Sound&#8221; was the title track and lead single from The Gaslight Anthem&#8217;s second album. Released in the summer of 2008, it became a critical hit if not a popular one. (It peaked at #35 on the Billboard Alternative chart.)</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/G1lq40tR72Q?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>The &#8217;59</strong> <strong>Sound</strong><br />\n<strong>First performed:</strong> June 27, 2009 (Pilton, England)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> June 28, 2009 (London, England)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 January 27, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce and Gaslight Anthem tear up \u201cThe \u201859 Sound\u201d at Hyde Park in 2009</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69651, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [3617, 5], "tags": [196, 1191, 195], "class_list": ["post-411", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-it-takes-two", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-59-sound", "tag-brian-fallon", "tag-gaslight-anthem"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/admin-ajax-99.jpg?fit=986%2C1000&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-6D", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-related-posts": [{"id": 57514, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/28/kingdom-of-days-june-28-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 411, "position": 0}, "title": "June 28", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 28, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "London Calling: Live in Hyde Park is filmed on this date, as is Bruce's video for \"Dancing in the Dark.\" Plus: a stormy night in Milan on the Rising Tour, a 1993 bar gig and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bruce-springsteenjpg-3ece188d0fb51648.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bruce-springsteenjpg-3ece188d0fb51648.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bruce-springsteenjpg-3ece188d0fb51648.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bruce-springsteenjpg-3ece188d0fb51648.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bruce-springsteenjpg-3ece188d0fb51648.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57513, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/27/kingdom-of-days-june-27-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 411, "position": 1}, "title": "June 27", "author": "Ken", "date": "June 27, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "For a rare song, \"Janey, Don't You Lose Heart\" is performed on two different occasions on this date. Plus: a complete 1982 bar gig, Bruce headlines Glastonbury, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/BS_LOST_BOX_cover_2000x2056.webp?fit=1168%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/BS_LOST_BOX_cover_2000x2056.webp?fit=1168%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/BS_LOST_BOX_cover_2000x2056.webp?fit=1168%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/BS_LOST_BOX_cover_2000x2056.webp?fit=1168%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/BS_LOST_BOX_cover_2000x2056.webp?fit=1168%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 62973, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/12/09/kingdom-of-days-december-9-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 411, "position": 2}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: December 9", "author": "Ken", "date": "December 9, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce surprises with a call-in to E Street Radio and a guest appearance with Gaslight Anthem, plus an emotional show the day after John Lennon's death. Much more inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/19801209_4_front-e1540575933488.jpg?fit=600%2C512&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/19801209_4_front-e1540575933488.jpg?fit=600%2C512&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/19801209_4_front-e1540575933488.jpg?fit=600%2C512&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []